  "texts": [
    "We combine all the logs from conversation sessions during the 14-day and 24-week study and evaluate CaiTI's system performance in this section.",
    "There are 454 conversation sessions with 18,309 and 2,013 segments of subjects' responses to CaiTI's original and follow-up questions, respectively.",
    "Some subjects answered the question with more than one sentence (segment).",
    "There are 107 times when the subjects failed to provide valid follow-up responses at the first attempt and triggered R-V Guide.",
    "CaiTI provides 2,013 empathic validation and support sessions with R-V Validator.As described in Section 5.4, CaiTI will conclude the CBT process, if the user does not provide a valid response after two attempts in each stage of the three-stage CBT process."
